WEBVTT

00:00:06.679 --> 00:00:11.251
Predstavljajte si vlak,
ki brez nadzora drvi po tirih,

00:00:11.251 --> 00:00:15.691
naravnost proti petim ujetim delavcem.

00:00:15.691 --> 00:00:17.909
Slučajno stojite poleg stikala,

00:00:17.909 --> 00:00:21.410
ki lahko vlak preusmeri na drugi tir.

00:00:21.410 --> 00:00:22.710
In tu je problem.

00:00:22.710 --> 00:00:27.799
Tudi na tem tiru je delavec, a samo eden.

00:00:27.799 --> 00:00:29.120
Kaj storiti?

00:00:29.120 --> 00:00:32.415
Boste žrtvovali eno življenje,
da jih rešite pet?